metadata.name: Dissolve
metadata.description:
The vastness called for her. 
It clearly called her name. 
"Come~"
She heard the rushing sound and followed its call, 
while the waves on the shore were pulling her deeper in.
"Come closer~"
"Should I really?" 
And yet she knew there was no going back anymore.
Her body went numb. Slowly.
Surrounded by all the colors she carried inside her.
And that is when she realized it.
"I'm finally with you!" - she said, before she dissolved for ever.
